{"author":{"id":"daecaa79b752289d08fa06c7a65c8d0387caf00b7e262b5741f4805727d0a582"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1722565960,"nonce":"hJt8IOQ5iM1XoA99E0DX8zd67zw=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOCGKeh86Rqnmz","github-url":"https://github.com/git-bug/git-bug/issues/1213","origin":"github"},"title":"Unified command syntax for UI components","message":"For simpler launching of both the web and terminal UI components, and to support better domain grouping, we should support a unified command syntax for launching the UIs.\n\n## Example commands\n\nLaunch the web UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui web [--port]\n```\n\nLaunch the TUI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui terminal\n```\n\nStore a preferred default UI (e.g. in git configuration)\n\n```\ngit bug ui set-default terminal\n```\n\nLaunch the configured default UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui\n```","files":null}]}